MooVaders!

A space Invaders clone built using Processing.

Processing is well worth checking out, and you'll need the package to complie this code.

To Install & run:

1. Download Processing from http://processing.org/download/

2. Make sure you've got a reasonably recent version of Java installed.  To do this go to your terminal / command prompt and type Java.  If it's there you'll see the version number, if not go get it (http://www.java.com/en/download/index.jsp for English version)

3. Open up any of the .pde files, and press the play button.

4. Mouse or key controls can be set int he options screen (a = left, d = right).

